snippet.title: Selling Sunset: Netflix Stories | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Welcome to The Oppenheim Group! As the newest agent at LA’s top luxury real estate brokerage, you'll need to sell your way up to win a dream listing.

Play Selling Sunset: Netflix Stories on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81774712

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 278 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Selling Sunset: Netflix Stories | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Rise to the top of LA's hottest real estate agency. Create your character and find glamour, success and romance in this interactive story game.
